# DETECT CCIRC - Scope Layer

## Overview

Scope Layer computes boolean scope columns (`scope_us`, `scope_fortis`, `scope_bcef`, `scope_japan`) based on source columns from the main CCIRC pipeline.

**Performance**: 30 seconds - 2 minutes (vs 2-4 hours for full pipeline re-run)

-----

## Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  CCIRC PIPELINE (run once to add source columns)                            │
│                                                                             │
│  Pre-processing ──► Detection ──► Post-processing ──► SP_display_seg       │
│       │                                                     │               │
│       └── Add 5 source columns                              │               │
│           • accounting_site_code_post_acc                   │               │
│           • pmas_code_post_acc                              │               │
│           • lb_site_risque_apres_accr                       │               │
│           • cd_uds_pmas_metier_ap_acc                       │               │
│           • business_country                                │               │
│                                                             │               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────┘
                                                              │
                                                              ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  SCOPE LAYER (run on each scope change - fast!)                             │
│                                                                             │
│  SP_display_seg ──► compute_scope_columns ──► SP_display_seg_scoped        │
│                            │                                                │
│                            │ Reads: ccirc_params.json["scopes"]            │
│                            │                                                │
│                            │ Computes:                                      │
│                            │   scope_us = acct_site IN (12309, 40043, ...) │
│                            │   scope_fortis = acct_site IN (10054, ...)    │
│                            │   scope_bcef = pmas='PMA_03' AND NOT IN ...   │
│                            │   scope_japan = acct_site IN (...) AND ...    │
│                                                                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

