## Scope Definitions

|Scope   |Filter Logic                                                                 |
|--------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|`us`    |`accounting_site_code_post_acc IN (12309, 40043, ...)`                       |
|`fortis`|`accounting_site_code_post_acc IN (10054, 10056, ...)`                       |
|`bcef`  |`pmas_code = 'PMA_03' AND (lb_site NOT IN ('BNPP Factor France') OR IS NULL)`|
|`japan` |`accounting_site_code IN (30448, 48019) AND pmas_code = 'PMA_05'`            |

