## Updating Scopes

### Add New Scope Values

Edit `ccirc_params.json`:

```json
{
  "scopes": {
    "us": {
      "filters": {
        "accounting_site_code_post_acc": {
          "operator": "IN",
          "values": ["12309", "40043", "NEW_CODE"]  ← Add here
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Re-run Scope Layer recipe (30 seconds).

### Add New Scope

```json
{
  "scopes": {
    "new_scope": {
      "label": "New Scope",
      "filters": {
        "column_name": {
          "operator": "IN",
          "values": ["value1", "value2"]
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

