## Output Columns

|Column        |Type   |Description                            |
|--------------|-------|---------------------------------------|
|`scope_us`    |Boolean|True if segment belongs to US scope    |
|`scope_fortis`|Boolean|True if segment belongs to Fortis scope|
|`scope_bcef`  |Boolean|True if segment belongs to BCeF scope  |
|`scope_japan` |Boolean|True if segment belongs to Japan scope |

**Note**: A segment can belong to multiple scopes (e.g., both `scope_us` and `scope_bcef` can be True).

