## Tableau Integration

Use scope columns as filters:

```sql
-- Single scope
SELECT * FROM SP_display_seg_scoped WHERE scope_us = true

-- Multiple scopes
SELECT * FROM SP_display_seg_scoped WHERE scope_us = true OR scope_bcef = true
```

Or use Tableau parameter + calculated field:

```
// Calculated field: Scope Filter
CASE [Scope Parameter]
  WHEN "All" THEN TRUE
  WHEN "US" THEN [scope_us]
  WHEN "Fortis" THEN [scope_fortis]
  WHEN "BCeF" THEN [scope_bcef]
  WHEN "Japan" THEN [scope_japan]
END
```

